<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>开闭原则 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%BC%80%E9%97%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99/</link><description>开闭原则 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%BC%80%E9%97%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>设计原则（SOLID+1）</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="设计原则solid1">设计原则（SOLID+1）</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：SOLID原则是面向对象设计的基石，通过单一职责、开闭、里氏替换、接口隔离、依赖倒置五个原则降低耦合提升内聚，加上组合复用原则形成完整的设计指导体系。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="solid1原则从职责划分扩展方式继承约束接口粒度依赖方向复用手段六个维度指导面向对象设计">SOLID+1原则从职责划分、扩展方式、继承约束、接口粒度、依赖方向、复用手段六个维度指导面向对象设计</h2>
<h3 id="单一职责原则srp">单一职责原则（SRP）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">❌ 一个类处理多个职责
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class UserService {
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    void register() {}      // 用户注册
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    void sendEmail() {}     // 发送邮件
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    void generateReport() {} // 生成报表
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">✅ 职责分离
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class UserService { void register() {} }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class EmailService { void sendEmail() {} }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class ReportService { void generateReport() {} }</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>要点</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>定义</td>
          <td>一个类只负责一项职责</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>判断标准</td>
          <td>类变更的原因是否只有一个</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>违反症状</td>
          <td>类代码行数过多、修改影响多个功能</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="开闭原则ocp">开闭原则（OCP）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">❌ 新增折扣类型需要修改原有代码
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">if (type.equals(&#34;VIP&#34;)) { price * 0.8; }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">else if (type.equals(&#34;SVIP&#34;)) { price * 0.6; }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">✅ 通过扩展实现
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">interface DiscountStrategy { double calculate(double price); }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class VIPDiscount implements DiscountStrategy { ... }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class SVIPDiscount implements DiscountStrategy { ... }</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>要点</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>定义</td>
          <td>对扩展开放，对修改关闭</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>实现方式</td>
          <td>抽象 + 多态</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>判断标准</td>
          <td>新增功能是否只需新增代码</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="里氏替换原则lsp">里氏替换原则（LSP）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">❌</span> <span class="err">子类改变了父类的行为约定</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="n">Rectangle</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="n">void</span> <span class="n">setWidth</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="ne">int</span> <span class="n">w</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="n">void</span> <span class="n">setHeight</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="ne">int</span> <span class="n">h</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="n">Square</span> <span class="k">extends</span> <span class="n">Rectangle</span> <span class="p">{</span>  <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">正方形不是长方形的正确子类</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="n">void</span> <span class="n">setWidth</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="ne">int</span> <span class="n">w</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="n">width</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">height</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">w</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="p">}</span>  <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">破坏了</span><span class="n">setHeight的语义</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">✅</span> <span class="err">正例：子类不改变父类契约</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="n">Bird</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="n">void</span> <span class="n">fly</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{}</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="n">Sparrow</span> <span class="k">extends</span> <span class="n">Bird</span> <span class="p">{}</span>      <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">麻雀会飞，符合</span><span class="n">LSP</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">企鹅不会飞，不应继承</span><span class="n">Bird</span><span class="err">，应继承更抽象的</span><span class="n">Animal</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>要点</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>定义</td>
          <td>子类必须能够替换父类而不影响程序正确性</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>判断标准</td>
          <td>继承是否合理（is-a关系）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>违反症状</td>
          <td>子类重写方法抛出异常或改变语义</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="接口隔离原则isp">接口隔离原则（ISP）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">❌ 胖接口强制实现不必要的方法
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">interface Worker { void work(); void eat(); }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class Robot implements Worker {  // 机器人不需要eat
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    void eat() { throw new UnsupportedOperationException(); }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">✅ 接口拆分
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">interface Workable { void work(); }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">interface Eatable { void eat(); }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class Robot implements Workable {}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class Human implements Workable, Eatable {}</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>要点</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>定义</td>
          <td>客户端不应依赖它不使用的接口</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>判断标准</td>
          <td>接口的实现类是否都需要所有方法</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="依赖倒置原则dip">依赖倒置原则（DIP）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">❌ 高层依赖低层具体实现
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class OrderService {
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    private MySqlRepository repository = new MySqlRepository();  // 直接依赖
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">✅ 依赖抽象
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">class OrderService {
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    private OrderRepository repository;  // 依赖接口
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    OrderService(OrderRepository repo) { this.repository = repo; }  // 注入
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">}</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>要点</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>定义</td>
          <td>高层模块不依赖低层模块，两者都依赖抽象</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>实现方式</td>
          <td>依赖注入（构造器/Setter/接口）</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="组合复用原则crp">组合复用原则（CRP）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">❌</span> <span class="err">通过继承复用（白箱复用，耦合高）</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="n">Vehicle</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="n">void</span> <span class="n">move</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{}</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="n">Car</span> <span class="k">extends</span> <span class="n">Vehicle</span> <span class="p">{}</span>  <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">继承是</span><span class="n">is</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">a关系</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">✅</span> <span class="err">通过组合复用（黑箱复用，耦合低）</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="n">Engine</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="n">void</span> <span class="n">start</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{}</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="n">Car</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="n">private</span> <span class="n">Engine</span> <span class="n">engine</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">组合是</span><span class="n">has</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">a关系</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="n">void</span> <span class="n">move</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="n">engine</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">start</span><span class="p">();</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>复用方式</th>
          <th>关系</th>
          <th>耦合度</th>
          <th>适用场景</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>继承</td>
          <td>is-a</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>真正的泛化关系</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>组合</td>
          <td>has-a</td>
          <td>低</td>
          <td>大多数场景首选</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1过度设计所有场景都套用原则">问题1：过度设计，所有场景都套用原则</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：为使用设计模式而使用，增加不必要的抽象
<strong>解决</strong>：先满足需求，在确实出现痛点时再重构，YAGNI原则</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>